Born

(1881 October 5) Sweden[3][4]

Summary

When Anna Matilda Bjork Pettersson was born on October 5, 1881, in Duvered, Västra Götaland, Sweden, her father, John, was 34, and her mother, Matilda, was 31. She had one brother and three sisters. She died on January 29, 1972, in Chicago, Illinois, at the age of 90, and was buried there.
